   <row>
    <id><![CDATA[21]]></id>
    <gid><![CDATA[5]]></gid>
    <group_name><![CDATA[Bedingungen und Filter]]></group_name>
    <description><![CDATA[<p>Limesurvey unterstützt eine Vielzahl von Bedingungen und Filtern zum Anzeigen und Vestecken von Fragen. Dies umfasst Bedingungen mit UND- sowie ODER-Verknüpfungen. Weitere Informationen finden sich in der <small><a href="manual.limesurvey.org/Conditions_Engine" lang="en" target="_blank">LimeSurvey Dokumentation</a></small>.</p>
]]></description>
    <language><![CDATA[de-informal]]></language>
    <sid><![CDATA[282267]]></sid>
    <group_order><![CDATA[6]]></group_order>
    <randomization_group/>
    <grelevance/>
   </row>
   <row>
    <id><![CDATA[22]]></id>
    <gid><![CDATA[5]]></gid>
    <group_name><![CDATA[Condition and scenario]]></group_name>
    <description><![CDATA[<p>LimeSurvey can use a lot of condition and filter to show or hide question. You an use AND or OR condition. You can use previous question answers and tokens.</p>

<p><small>More information : <a href="http://manual.limesurvey.org/Conditions_Engine">Conditions Engine</a> and <a href="http://manual.limesurvey.org/Expression_Manager">expression manager</a></small></p>
]]></description>
    <language><![CDATA[en]]></language>
    <sid><![CDATA[282267]]></sid>
    <group_order><![CDATA[6]]></group_order>
    <randomization_group/>
    <grelevance/>
   </row>
   <row>
    <id><![CDATA[23]]></id>
    <gid><![CDATA[5]]></gid>
    <group_name><![CDATA[Conditions et scenarios]]></group_name>
    <description><![CDATA[<p>LimeSurvey peut utiliser de nombreuses conditions et filtres pour masquer certaines questions. Il est possible d'utiliser des conditions de type OR ou AND. Vous pouvez utiliser les réponses précédentes mais aussi les attributs des invitations.</p>

<p><small>Plus d'informations : <a href="http://manual.limesurvey.org/Conditions_Engine">le gestionnaire de conditions</a> et le <a href="http://manual.limesurvey.org/Expression_Manager">gestionnaire d'expressions</a></small></p>
]]></description>
    <language><![CDATA[fr]]></language>
    <sid><![CDATA[282267]]></sid>
    <group_order><![CDATA[6]]></group_order>
    <randomization_group/>
    <grelevance/>
   </row>
   <row>
    <id><![CDATA[24]]></id>
    <gid><![CDATA[5]]></gid>
    <group_name><![CDATA[Condizioni e scenari]]></group_name>
    <description><![CDATA[<p>LimeSurvey consente l'utilizzo di molte condizioni e filtri per nascondere e mostrare domande. Puoi usare le condizioni in AND e in OR, e utilizzare le risposte fornite alle domande precedenti oppure le informazioni dei partecipanti (tokens).</p>
<small>Ulteriori informazioni : <a href="http://manual.limesurvey.org/Conditions_Engine">Conditions Engine</a> e <a href="http://manual.limesurvey.org/Expression_Manager">expression manager</a></small>]]></description>
    <language><![CDATA[it]]></language>
    <sid><![CDATA[282267]]></sid>
    <group_order><![CDATA[6]]></group_order>
    <randomization_group/>
    <grelevance/>
   </row>
   <row>
    <id><![CDATA[26]]></id>
    <gid><![CDATA[6]]></gid>
    <group_name><![CDATA[Filter]]></group_name>
    <description><![CDATA[Antwortoptionen von Folgefragen können durch das Frageattribut <a href="http://manual.limesurvey.org/QS:Array_filter" lang="en" target="_blank">Array Filter</a><a> und </a><a href="http://manual.limesurvey.org/Array_filter_exclude" lang="en" target="_blank">Array Filter Exclusion</a> gefiltert werden.]]></description>
    <language><![CDATA[de-informal]]></language>
    <sid><![CDATA[282267]]></sid>
    <group_order><![CDATA[7]]></group_order>
    <randomization_group/>
    <grelevance/>
   </row>
   <row>
    <id><![CDATA[27]]></id>
    <gid><![CDATA[6]]></gid>
    <group_name><![CDATA[Filter]]></group_name>
    <description><![CDATA[You can display/hide subquestion with <a href="http://manual.limesurvey.org/QS:Array_filter" lang="en" target="_blank">Array Filter</a> and <a href="http://manual.limesurvey.org/QS:Array_filter_exclude" lang="en" target="_blank">Array Filter Exclusion</a>. We use Expression Manager to hide and show question too.]]></description>
    <language><![CDATA[en]]></language>
    <sid><![CDATA[282267]]></sid>
    <group_order><![CDATA[7]]></group_order>
    <randomization_group/>
    <grelevance/>
   </row>
   <row>
    <id><![CDATA[28]]></id>
    <gid><![CDATA[6]]></gid>
    <group_name><![CDATA[Filtres de tableaux]]></group_name>
    <description><![CDATA[Vous pouvez afficher ou masquer une série de sous question avec l'attribut <a href="http://manual.limesurvey.org/QS:Array_filter" lang="en" target="_blank">Filtre de tableau</a> et <a href="http://manual.limesurvey.org/QS:Array_filter_exclude" lang="en" target="_blank">Filttre d’exclusion</a>. On utilise le gestionnaire d'expression pour masquer ou montrer les questions correspondantes.]]></description>
    <language><![CDATA[fr]]></language>
    <sid><![CDATA[282267]]></sid>
    <group_order><![CDATA[7]]></group_order>
    <randomization_group/>
    <grelevance/>
   </row>
   <row>
    <id><![CDATA[29]]></id>
    <gid><![CDATA[6]]></gid>
    <group_name><![CDATA[Filtri]]></group_name>
    <description><![CDATA[E' possibile nascondere/mostrare sottodomande usando i <a href="http://manual.limesurvey.org/QS:Array_filter" lang="en" target="_blank">Filtri Array</a> and <a href="http://manual.limesurvey.org/QS:Array_filter_exclude" lang="en" target="_blank">Filtri Array di Esclusione</a>. Useremo anche l'Expression Manager per nascondere e mostrare domande.]]></description>
    <language><![CDATA[it]]></language>
    <sid><![CDATA[282267]]></sid>
    <group_order><![CDATA[7]]></group_order>
    <randomization_group/>
    <grelevance/>
   </row>
